txt.en: <u>The Hold of Kála-murg</u>\n\qOne of the last hold outs of Orcs in Lhingris, the well fortified encampment of Kála-murg continues to be battered by Ungol forces.\q
With the spiders in retreat, you should confront the foes within the caverns.
More spiders terrorize the inner encampment
A small band of Orcs have barricaded themselves in these caverns
